Package burlap.oomdp.core

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AbstractGroundedAction
    This is an interface for grounded actions.
    AbstractObjectParameterizedGroundedAction
    An interface extension to the AbstractGroundedAction interface for grounded actions whose parameter included references to OO-MDP ObjectInstances.
    TerminalFunction
    And interface for defining terminal states of an MDP.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractObjectParameterizedGroundedAction.Helper  
    Attribute
    The attribute class defines attributes that define OO-MDP object classes.
    Domain
    This is the base class for a problem domain.
    GroundedProp
    Propositional functions are defined to be evaluated on object parameters and this class provides a definition for a grounded propositional function; that is, it specifies specific object parameters on which the propositional function should be evaluated.
    ObjectClass
    Object classes are part of the OO-MDP definition and define the kinds of objects that can exist in an OO-MDP state.
    PropositionalFunction
    The propositional function class defines evaluations of object instances in an OO-MDP state and are part of the definition for an OO-MDP domain.
    TransitionProbability
    Represents the probability of transition to a given state.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Attribute.AttributeType
    And enumeration type to indicate the various types of attributes supported.
